00:00:46.300 --> 00:00:49.540
topics that are going to be covered by the seven abstract.

14
00:00:50.070 --> 00:00:53.720
The first abstract on the wide genomic characterization of pre-cancer

15
00:00:53.800 --> 00:00:57.180
lesions, discerning between

16
