1281
01:16:05.736 --> 01:16:06.116
So

1282
01:16:07.096 --> 01:16:10.676
it was considered

1283
01:16:10.796 --> 01:16:11.096
that

1284
01:16:13.896 --> 01:16:17.616
this result is partly relevant

1285
01:16:17.636 --> 01:16:18.136
to

1286
01:16:19.676 --> 01:16:19.685
the

1287
01:16:21.016 --> 01:16:24.676
